# 🚀 Smart Task Manager

A production-grade full-stack task management application with AI features, real-time updates, and cloud deployment.

## 🌐 Live Demo
https://smart-task-manager-one-lake.vercel.app

## ✨ Features
- 🔐 JWT Authentication + Role Based Access Control
- ⚡ Real-time updates with WebSockets
- 🤖 AI task suggestions powered by LLaMA 3 (Groq)
- ⏰ Automated CRON jobs for overdue detection
- 🌍 Multi-language support (EN, ES, FR)
- 🐳 Dockerized with Jenkins CI/CD pipeline
- ☁️ Deployed on AWS EC2 with Nginx + SSL

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: React, Vite, Tailwind CSS
Backend: Node.js, Express, Prisma
Database: PostgreSQL
Real-time: Socket.IO
DevOps: Docker, Jenkins, AWS EC2, Nginx